196
00:08:24,500 --> 00:08:25,380
欢迎
Welcome.

197
00:08:25,420 --> 00:08:28,000
-你好  谢谢  -斯科特
- Hi. Thank you. - Scottie.

198
00:08:28,000 --> 00:08:29,680
