Number one at studying.

205
00:08:38,750 --> 00:08:40,270
好了  这边请
Okay, this way.

206
00:08:41,620 --> 00:08:42,920
告诉我  斯科特
Tell me, Scottie,

207
00:08:43,070 --> 00:08:45,450
当我们真正对峙公堂时
What's my success rate against you in the real world

