You chose to work with the one guy who's going against me.

246
00:10:36,000 --> 00:10:37,400
凯尔征求我意见  我同意了
Kyle asked me, and I said yes.

247
00:10:37,410 --> 00:10:37,840
算了
You know what?

248
00:10:37,840 --> 00:10:39,940
无所谓  反正你也没机会出庭作证
It doesn't really matter,'cause you're never gonna take the stand.

249
00:10:39,940 --> 00:10:41,040
是吗  为什么
Really? How's that?

250
00:10:41,130 --> 00:10:42,080
等着瞧吧
It's a surprise.

251
00:10:42,600 --> 00:10:44,980
准备期待模拟庭审传奇的诞生吧
But prepare to watch a mock trial legend be born.

