We'd like to submit a settlement agreement--

254
00:10:53,990 --> 00:10:55,420
原告律师准备就绪  法官大人
The plaintiff is ready, your honor.

255
00:10:56,620 --> 00:10:57,810
到底谁说了算  律师
Which is it, counselor?

256
00:10:58,860 --> 00:11:00,760
原告律师和我
The counsel for the plaintiff

257
00:11:00,760 --> 00:11:02,890
昨天达成调解共识
and I agreed to a settlement yesterday.

258
00:11:02,940 --> 00:11:04,790
他肯定是误会了  我们是讨论过
He must've misunderstood. We had discussed,

259
00:11:04,790 --> 00:11:06,120
