But in any case, due diligence is a requirement.

306
00:13:06,550 --> 00:13:08,290
我对我的委托人有义务
I have an obligation to my client.

307
00:13:10,240 --> 00:13:11,350
那我们没法达成协议了
Then we don't have a deal.

308
00:13:12,580 --> 00:13:15,130
大家都会知道是你否了这个协议
And everyone's gonna know it's because you killed it.

309
00:13:15,570 --> 00:13:16,530
知道吗...
You know...

310
00:13:17,240 --> 00:13:19,510
看来你并不急着把你们的内部账簿给我们看
I don't see you rushing to show us your private books.

311
00:13:19,510 --> 00:13:20,930
我没什么好隐瞒的
I have nothing to hide.

312
00:13:21,100 --> 00:13:23,190
你现在完全可以看我们的账簿
You can have full access to our books right now.

313
00:13:23,190 --> 00:13:25,130
很好  你给我看你们的  我给你看我们的
Great. You show me yours, and I'll show you mine.

314
00:13:26,180 --> 00:13:27,900
别说出来  哈维
Don't say it, Harvey.

315
00:13:30,690 --> 00:13:31,500
迈克
Mike.

316
00:13:32,570 --> 00:13:35,090
-你没事吧  -现在你关心我了
- Hey, are you okay? - Now you care?

317
00:13:35,090 --> 00:13:36,440
罗斯先生  我要警告你
Mr. Ross, I'm gonna have to ask you

318
00:13:36,440 --> 00:13:37,550
不能和我的委托人说话
not to speak to my client.

319
00:13:37,550 --> 00:13:38,600
她不是你的委托人
She's not your client.

320
00:13:38,600 --> 00:13:40,120
她是律师助理瑞秋
She is Rachel the paralegal.

321
00:13:40,120 --> 00:13:42,740
我只有五分钟准备  你最好赶紧从我面前消失
And I only have five minutes, so you should really get out of my face.

322
00:13:42,740 --> 00:13:44,250
-你有什么问题吗  迈克  -我的问题是
- What's your problem, Mike? - My problem is that

