00:13:44,250 --> 00:13:46,730
你没胆量来一场公平的较量  凯尔
you don't have the balls to make this a fair fight, Kyle.

324
00:13:46,730 --> 00:13:48,280
律师这行就没有公平竞争之说
Lawyering isn't about fighting fair,

325
00:13:48,280 --> 00:13:49,970
你最好不要诬告陷害
and you'd better watch your false accusations,

326
00:13:50,030 --> 00:13:52,200
否则我要告你诽谤
or I might just sue you for defamation.

327
00:13:53,000 --> 00:13:54,070
跟我来
Come on.

328
00:13:58,210 --> 00:14:00,060
被告方想要反诉
The defendant wishes to countersue.

329
00:13:58,210 --> 00:14:00,060
反诉:简单地说就是在民事诉讼中  被告反告原告

330
00:14:00,060 --> 00:14:00,980
理由呢
On what grounds?

331
00:14:00,980 --> 00:14:03,130
我觉得那是我该说的话  律师
 I believe that's my line, counselor.

332
00:14:03,950 --> 00:14:05,460
毁损名誉
Defamation of character.

333
00:14:05,800 --> 00:14:07,560
原告的录像给莉娜・兰德斯
The plaintiff's video negatively impacted

334
00:14:07,560 --> 00:14:09,020
带来了极其负面的影响
the perception of Lena Lunders

335
00:14:09,020 --> 00:14:10,520
