and impaired her financial well-being.

336
00:14:10,520 --> 00:14:11,660
那太荒唐了  法官大人
That's ridiculous, your honor.

337
00:14:11,660 --> 00:14:13,050
为了诽谤中伤我的委托人
In order for there to be defamation,

338
00:14:13,050 --> 00:14:14,930
