Then you should have no problem proving that in court.

341
00:14:20,780 --> 00:14:22,270
反诉成立
The countersuit is allowed.

342
00:14:22,330 --> 00:14:23,080
你是认真的吗
Are you serious?

343
00:14:23,080 --> 00:14:24,830
你是不是想要到法官席前
Would you like to approach the bench

344
00:14:24,830 --> 00:14:26,420
看看我到底有多认真
