350
00:14:40,270 --> 00:14:43,560
以免你们有人提出反诉
just because we assumed one of you would.

351
00:14:44,150 --> 00:14:45,820
所以我批准该请求
So I'm going to allow it.

352
00:14:46,000 --> 00:14:47,890
你对此有意见吗
Do you have a problem with that?

353
00:14:48,280 --> 00:14:49,500
没有  法官大人
No, your honor.

354
00:14:49,590 --> 00:14:51,490
